hadiths[25]{hadithnumber,text}:
2270,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab zamana qarib ho jaeyga padhi. to momin key khuwab kam hi jhootey hongey, un mein sab sey ziyada sachey khuwab wala wo hoga jiski baaten ziyada sachi hongi , musalman ka khuwab nabuwat ka chhiyaaliswan hissa hai padhi. khuwab teen qism key hotey hain, behtar aur achey khuwab Allah ki taraf sey basharat hotey hain, kuch khuwab shetan ki taraf sey takleef o ranj ka baais hotey hain, aur kuch khuwab aadmi key dil key khayalat hotey hain, lihaza jab tum mein sey koi aisa khuwab dekhey jisey wo napasand karta hai to khada ho kar thookey aur usey logon sey na bayan karey '' , aap ney farmaya : ''main khuwab mein qaid (pair mein bedi pehanna) pasand karta hun aur toq ko napasand karta hun, qaid sey murad Deen par Sabit qadmi hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2271,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' momin ka khuwab nabuwat ka chhiyaaliswan hissa hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ubada ki hadees sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , abu-Rizeen Uqeli , abu Saeed Khudri , Abdullah bin Amr , Auf bin Malik , ibne-Umar aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2272,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''risaalat aur nabuwat ka silsila khatam ho chuka hai, lihaza merey baad koi Rasool aur koi Nabi na hoga'', Anas kehtey hain : ye baat logon par giraan guzri to aap ney farmaya : ''albatta basharatein baqi hain'' , Sahaba ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool! basharatein kya hain? aap ney farmaya : ''musalman ka khuwab aur ye nabuwat ka eik hissa hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey yani Mukhtaar bin fulful ki riwayat sey Hasan sahih gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , Huzefa bin Usaid , ibne-Abbas , Umme Kurz aur abu-Usaid (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2273,"mainey Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey Allah Taala key us qol « لهم البشرى في الحياة الدنيا » '' unkey liye duniyaawi zindagi mein basharat hai'' ( Yunus : ۶۴ ( key barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : jab sey mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey uskey barey mein puchha hai, tumharey siwa sirf eik aadmi ney mujh sey puchha hai, mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey uskey barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : '' jab sey ye aayat nazil hui hai uskey barey main tumharey siwa kisi ney nahin puchha , is sey murad nek aur achey khuwab hain jisey musalman dekhta hai ya usey dikhaya jata hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Ubada bin Samit (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2274,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''sachay khuwab wo hain jo sehri ( subh ( key waqt aatey hain ''.
2275,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey Allah Taala ki aayate-kareema : « لهم البشرى في الحياة الدنيا » key barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : ''is sey murad achey aur nek khuwab hain jisey momin dekhta hai ya usey dikhaya jata hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- Harab ney apni hadees mein Yahya bin abi Kasir sey «Anana» key bajaey hadees bayan karney key tareeqe « حدثني » key tariqey key sath riwayat ki hai."
2276,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney mujhey khuwab mein dekha usney mujhey hi dekha , isliye ke shetan meri shakal ikhtiyar nahin kar sakta hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , abu-Qatada , ibne-Abbas , abu Saeed Khudri , Jabir , Anas , abu Malik Ashjai key walid , abu-Bakra aur abu-Hujefa (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2277,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' achey khuwab Allah ki taraf sey hotey hain, aur burey khuwab shetan ki taraf sey, lihaza jab tum mein sey koi na-pasandida khuwab dekhey to teen baar apney baain taraf thookey aur uskey shar sey Allah ki panah maangey, aisa karney par wo usey nuqsan nahin pahuncha sakta hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr , abu-Saeed , Jabir aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2278,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' momin ka khuwab nabuwat ka chaliswan hissa hai aur khuwab ki jab tak tabeer na bayan ki jaey wo eik perindey key panjey mein hota hai, phir jab tabeer bayan kar di jati hai to wo waqey ho jata hai'' , abu-Rizeen kehtey hain : mera khayal hai aap ney ye bhi farmaya : '' khuwab sirf us sey bayan karo jo aqlmand ho ya jis sey tumhari dosti ho ''."
2279,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' musalman ka khuwab nabuwat ka chhiyaaliswan hissa hota hai aur khuwab ki jab tak tabeer na bayan ki jaey wo eik perindey key panjey mein hota hai phir jab tabeer bayan kar di jati hai to wo waqey ho jata hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- abu-Rizeen Uqeli ka naam laqeet bin Aamir hai, 3- Hammad bin Salma ney isey Yala bin Ata sey riwayat kartey huye '' Wakee bin Hadas'' kaha hai jabke Shoba, abu Awana aur Hushem ney isey Yala bin Ata sey riwayat kartey huye '' Wakee bin Adas'' kaha hai aur ye ziyada sahih hai."
2280,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' khuwab teen qism key hotey hain, eik khuwab wo hai jo sacha hota hai, eik khuwab wo hai ke aadmi jo kuch sochta rehta hai, usi ko khuwab mein dekhta hai, aur eik khuwab aisa hai jo shetan ki taraf sey hota hai aur gham o sadmey ka sabab hota hai, lihaza jo shakhs khuwab mein koi naa-pasandida chiz dekhey to usey chahiye ke wo uth kar namaz padhey , aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam kaha kartey they : '' mujhey khuwab mein bedi ka dekhna achcha lagta hai aur toq dekhney ko mein napasand karta hun, bedi ki tabeer Deen par Sabit qadmi ( jamey rehna ( hai'' , aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam kaha kartey they : '' jisney khuwab mein mujhey dekha to wo main hi hun, isliye ke shetan meri shakal nahin apna sakta hai'' , aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam farmaya kartey they : '' khuwab kisi aalim ya khairkhaah sey hi bayan kya jaey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Anas, abu-Bakra, Umme Ulaa, ibne-Umar , Aaisha , abu-Musa , Jabir , abu Saeed Khudri , ibne-Abbas aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2281,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs jhoota khuwab bayan kerey. qiyamat key din usey jo key darmiyan gireh laganey par mukallaf kya jaeyga ''.
2282,"Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key wastey sey usi jaisi hadees riwayat kartey hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- ye hadees pehli hadees sey ziyada sahih hai, padhi. 3- is bab mein ibne-Abbas , Abu-Hurera , abu-Shuraih aur Waasila (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2283,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs jhoota khuwab bayan karey to qiyamat key din do jo key darmiyan gireh laganey par mukallaf kya jaeyga aur wo un dono key darmiyan gireh hergiz nahin laga sakega''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
2284,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : ''main soyaa huwa tha ke us doran merey paas doodh ka eik piyala laya gaya, mainey us sey piya phir apna jutha umr bin Khattab ko dey diya, Sahaba ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! aap ney uski kya tabeer ki ? '' farmaya : '' ilm sey '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar ki hadees sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , abu-Bakra , ibne-Abbas , Abdullah bin Salam , Khuzaima , Tufail bin Sakhbara, abu-Umama aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
2285,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main soyaa huwa tha dekha : log merey samney pesh kiye ja rahey hain aur wo qamis pehney huye hain, baaz ki qamis chhaati tak pahunch rahi thi aur baaz ki ussey nichey tak pahunch rahi thi, phir merey samney umr ko pesh kya gaya unkey jism par jo qamis thi wo usey ghaseet rahey they'', Sahaba ney arz kya : Allah key Rasool! aap ney uski kya tabeer ki ? aap ney farmaya : '' Deen sey '' padhi. ."
2286,abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey usi jaisi aur usi maana ki hadees riwayat kartey hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye ziyada sahih hai.
2287,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik din farmaya : '' tum mein sey kis ney khuwab dekha hai? '' eik aadmi ney kaha : mainey dekha ke aasman sey eik tarazu utra , aap aur abu-Bakar toley gaey to aap abu-Bakar sey bhari nikley, abu-Bakar aur umr toley gaey, to abu-Bakar bhari nikley , umr aur Usman toley gaey to umr bhari nikley phir tarazu utha liya gaya, abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : hamney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key chehrey par nagawari key aasaar dekhay. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2288,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey Warqa ( Warqa bin Naufal ( key barey mein puchha gaya to khadeeja ney kaha : unhoney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki tasdeeq ki thi magar wo aap ki nabuwat key zuhoor sey pehley wafat paa gaey, ye sun kar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' mujhey khuwab mein unhen dikhaya gaya hai, us waqt unkey jism par safed kapdey they, agar wo jahannami hotey to unkey jism par koi doosra libas hota '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- muhaddeseen key nazdik Usman bin Abdur-Rehman qawi nahin hain."
2289,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key us khuwab key barey mein marvi hai jis mein aap ney abu-Bakar aur umr ko dekha , aap ney farmaya : ''main ney dekha ke log (eik kunwen par) jama ho gaey hain, phir abu-Bakar ney eik ya do dol kheenchey aur unkey khinchney mein kamzori thi Allah un ki maghfirat karey , phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) khadey huye aur unhoney dol khincha to wo dol badey dol mein badal gaya, mainey kisi mazbut aur taqatwar shakhs ko nahin dekha jisney aisa kaam kya ho, yahan tak ke logon ney apni aaram gaahon mein jagah pakdi'' (yani sab aasooda ho gaey). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki riwayat sey sahih gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
2290,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key khuwab key barey mein riwayat hai, aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main ney paraaganda baalon wali eik kaali aurat ko dekha jo Madina sey nikli aur Mahya mein thehar gaee (Mahya, Johfa ka doosra naam hai) , mainey uski tabeer ye ki ke wo Madina ki (bukhaar wali) wabaa hai jo Johfa chali jaeygi ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
2291,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' aakhir waqt mein momin key khuwab kam hi jhootey hongey , aur khuwab un logon ka sacha hoga jinki baaten ziyada sachi hongi , khuwab teen qism key hotey hain : achey khuwab jo Allah ki taraf sey basharat hotey hain, wo khuwab jisey insan dil mein sochta rehta hai, aur wo khuwab jo shetan ki taraf sey hota hai aur gham ka sabab hota hai, lihaza jab tum mein sey koi naa-pasandida khwaab dekhey to usey kisi sey bayan na kerey. usey chahiye ke uth kar namaz padhey'' , Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : main khuwab mein qaid dekhna achcha samajhta hun aur bedi dekhna bura samajhta hun, qaid ki tabeer Sabit qadmi hai, Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' momin ka khuwab nabuwat ka chhiyaaliswan hissa hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Abdul-Wahaab Saqafi ney Ayub sey ye hadees marfooan riwayat ki hai aur Hammad bin Zaid ney Ayub sey usey moqufan riwayat kya hai."
2292,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''mainey khuwab mein dekha ke merey haath mein soney key do kangan hain, unkey haal ney mujhey gham mein dal diya, phir mujhey wahi ki gaee ke main un par phunkun, lihaza mainey phunka to wo dono aad gaey, mainey un dono kanganon ki tabeer (nabuwat ka daawa karney waley) do jhooton sey ki jo merey baad niklengey : eik ka naam Musailma hoga jo yamaama ka rehney wala hoga aur doosrey ka naam Ansaa hoga, jo Sanaa ka rehney wala hoga '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih gharib hai."
2293,"Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey they : eik aadmi ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar kaha : mainey raat ko khuwab mein badal ka eik tukda dekha jis sey ghi aur shehad tapak raha tha, aur logon ko mainey dekha wo apney haathon mein ley kar usey pi rahey hain, kisi ney ziyada piya aur kisi ney kam, aur mainey eik rassi dekhi jo aasman sey zamin tak latak rahi thi, Allah key Rasool ! aur mainey aap ko dekha ke aap wo rassi pakad kar ooper chaley gaey, phir aap key baad eik aur shakhs usey pakad kar ooper chala gaya, phir uskey baad eik aur shakhs ney pakada aur wo bhi ooper chala gaya, phir usey eik aur aadmi ney pakda to rassi toot gaee , phir wo jod di gaee to wo bhi ooper chala gaya, abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Allah key Rasool ! - merey maan-baap aap par qurban hon, Allah ki qism ! mujhey uski tabeer bayan karney ki ijazat dijiye , aap ney farmaya : '' bayan karo '' , abu-Bakar ney kaha : abr key tukdey sey murad Islam hai aur us sey jo ghi aur shehad tapak raha tha wo Quran hai aur uski Shirni aur narmi murad hai, ziyada aur kam peeney walon sey murad Quran hasil karney waley hain, aur aasman sey zamin tak latakney wali us rassi sey murad haq hai jis par aap qaaim hain, aap usey pakdey huye hain phir Allah Taala aap ko ooper utha leyga , phir uskey baad eik aur aadmi pakdega aur wo bhi pakad kar ooper chadh jaeyga, uskey baad eik aur aadmi pakdega , to wo bhi pakad kar ooper chadh jaeyga, phir uskey baad eik teesra aadmi pakdega to rassi toot jaeygi, phir uskey liye jod di jaeygi aur wo bhi chadh jaeyga, Allah key Rasool ! bataiye mainey sahih bayan kya ya ghalat ? Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum ney kuch sahih bayan kya aur kuch ghalat , abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : merey maan-baap aap par qurban ! main qism deta hun aap bataiye mainey kya ghalati ki hai? Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' qism na dilaao'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
2294,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab hamen Fajr padha kar farigh hotey to logon ki taraf mutawajjeh hotey aur farmatey : ''kya tum mein sey kisi ney aaj raat koi khuwab dekha hai?''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ye hadees eik taweel qissey key zimn mein Auf aur Jareer bin Hazim sey marvi hai, jisey ye dono Rajaa sey, Rajaa, Samra sey aur Samra Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain 3- Muhammad bin Bashaar ney isi tarah ye hadees Wahab bin Jareer sey ikhtisaar key sath riwayat ki hai."
